snippet.title: Game Boy Longplay [334] Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade (US)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: KAGE-008

Port of the NES game, specifically the Ubisoft version.

As in the movie, the player's quest is to find the Holy Grail. En route, the player must find the Cross of Coronado, the Knight of the First Crusade's Shield and Henry Jones Sr.'s Grail Diary.

Bad ending is attached right after the good ending and credits roll.

Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
